Setup Package Build Environment
-------------------------------
  * create clean new user
  * modify .bashrc:

----
# use the local lib perl modules
eval $(perl -I$HOME/perl5/lib/perl5 -Mlocal::lib)
export PERL5LIB="$HOME/perl5/lib/perl5'
export PERL_MM_OPT='INSTALL_BASE=$HOME/perl5
INSTALLARCHLIB=$HOME/perl5/lib/perl5
INSTALLSITEARCH=$HOME/perl5/lib/perl5
INSTALLVENDORARCH=$HOME/perl5/lib/perl5"
----

  * git clone repository
  * run ./script/thruk_create_package.pl
